Package: dpmclust
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Nonparametric Clustering Using 'DP-means' Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mikhail", "Popov", email = "mikhail@mpopov.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = "@bearloga on Twitter")
    )
Description: Implements the k-means-like clustering 'DP-means' algorithm by
    Kulis and Jordan (2011) which enables Bayesian nonparametric clustering
    with the unknown number of clusters determined automatically by setting
    a threshold which controls when a new cluster should be created.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
